				Committed to Earning Your Trust
			










Imagine New Goals






YOUR GOALS, FIRST AND FOREMOST






Legg Mason combines its passion for championing the long-term goals of individual and institutional investors with the distinct expertise of nine principal investment firms. Through ongoing product innovation and steadfast client service, we’ve become a world leader in asset management.












		    	key highlights
		    	
		    	
		    








Legg Mason’s assets under management as of March 31, 2017 were $728 billion.
 















 










Legg Mason’s gross revenues for Fiscal Fourth Quarter 2017 were $723.1 million.




















