Dublin Domiciled





 



Dublin Domiciled Funds
Legg Mason Global Funds Plc

Our Dublin based fund range, known as Legg Mason Global Funds plc, brings together a collection of fixed income, equity and equity income funds covering a range of strategies and world markets. 


Legg Mason Global Funds plc is an umbrella fund established as an open-ended investment company with variable capital incorporated with limited liability under the laws of Ireland. It qualifies, and is authorised, in Ireland by the Financial Regulator as an undertaking for collective investment in transferable securities and qualifies for distributor status.






